---
headerTitle: Employer Routed Funding
---

<div class="grid-wrapper">
  	<main role="main" class="grid grid-2-3">
		<header>
			<h1 class="heading-xlarge">Estimate your funding</h1>
			<p>Find out how much funding you're entitled to by searching for your apprentice below.</p>
		</header>
		<article>
			<form id="standardSearchForm" method="POST" action="/employer/search.html">
				<fieldset>
					<div class="form-group">
    					<label class="heading-small" for="Keywords">Which job title would your apprentice have?</label>
    					<p class="font-xsmall">Different apprenticeship standards are funded differently</p>
						
						<input  autofocus="autofocus" class="form-control" data-val="true" data-val-regex="'Keywords' contains some invalid characters" data-val-regex-pattern="^[a-zA-Z]+$" id="Standard" name="Standard" type="search" value="">
					</div>
					<div class="form-group">
    					<label class="heading-small" for="Postcode">What is your businesses postcode?</label>
    					<p class="font-xsmall">We will help you find providers close to your area</p>
						
						<input autofocus="" class="form-control" data-val="true" data-val-regex="'Keywords' contains some invalid characters" data-val-regex-pattern="^[a-zA-Z0-9]+$" id="Postcode" name="Postcode" type="search" value="">
					</div>
					<div class="form-group">
    					<label class="heading-small" for="Size">Do you have 50 or more employees?</label>
    					<p class="font-xsmall">Small businesses are entitled to more funding</p>

					    <label for="SizeAbove50Yes" class="block-label"><input type="radio" name="SizeAbove50" value="1" id="SizeAbove50Yes"/> Yes</label></li>
					    <label for="SizeAbove50No" class="block-label"><input type="radio" name="SizeAbove50" value="0" id="SizeAbove50No"/> No</label></li>

					</div>
					<div class="form-group">
    					<label class="heading-small" for="ApprenticeAge">Do you consider apprentice under 18 years old?</label>
    					<p class="font-xsmall">Hiring younger apprentice may mean more funding</p>

					    <label for="ApprenticeAgeUnder18Yes" class="block-label"> <input type="radio" name="ApprenticeAgeUnder18" value="1" id="ApprenticeAgeUnder18Yes" /> Yes</label>
					    <label for="ApprenticeAgeUnder18No" class="block-label"> <input type="radio" name="ApprenticeAgeUnder18" value="0" id="ApprenticeAgeUnder18No" />No</label>
					    <label for="ApprenticeAgeUnder18NotSure" class="block-label"> <input type="radio" name="ApprenticeAgeUnder18" value="" id="ApprenticeAgeUnder18NotSure" />Not sure</label>

					</div>
					<div class="get-started">
						<button type="submit" class="button">Estimate your funding</button>
					</div>
				</fieldset>
			</form>
		</article>
  	</main>
  	<div class="related-container grid grid-1-3">
		<div class="related">
	  		{{> info-links}}
  		</div>
  	</div>
</div>  